For updates on the country's p2p developments, see http://del.icio.us/mbauwens/P2P-Netherlands

We also have the [http://blognl.p2pfoundation.net/ Dutch P2P blog], currently inactive.

Our Dutch-language material is [http://p2pfoundation.net/Category:Dutch here].


